  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Packet
    This class is a container of Units and is used as the basic Resource reference in all the Game
    PacketTest
    Class used to test the ResourcePacket package to know if the Unit class and the Packet class works great
    Unit
    Class that represents the single Resource Unit of the Game, it has a Resource type and a quantity
